title: New Creator: Xtina Holder
body:

Info:
Christina Holder is a DC-based finance professional and creator of Womxn in Business, the largest club for women on Clubhouse. 

Use Cases:
Distribution - coin distribution to founding club members and other VIPs - Transaction use - Users to pay coins to host their event in her CH club, with coin rebates to those who have audiences that hit a certain size  
Add'l use cases - Sponsor-driven coin distributions, donations, umbrella coin for other women-based clubs and influencers to leverage 

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1,000

A 'yes' will approve Xtina with a $1,000 Community Treasury Gift Coin grant.

A 'no' will deny this proposal.
